description: Dell PowerScale OneFS, 8.0.x-9.5.x, contains an improper handling of insufficient privileges vulnerability. A local  privileged attacker could potentially exploit this vulnerability, leading to elevation of privilege and affect in compliance mode also.

enisaIdProduct.product_version: Version 9.2.1.0 through 9.2.1.22 , Version 9.4.0.0 through 9.4.0.13, Version 9.5.0.0 through 9.5.0.3
